  <summary date="2019-02-14T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">EAGLES Act of 2019

This bill provides statutory authority for the National Threat Assessment Center (NTAC) within the Department of Homeland Security.

It authorizes the functions of NTAC through FY2023 and expands them to include the establishment of a national program on targeted school violence prevention.</summary>
